(0, 'document', 'Java简介', '{"content":"# Java简介与环境设置\n\n## 什么是Java\nJava是一门面向对象的编程语言，由Sun Microsystems于1995年发布。Java具有跨平台、安全性高、简单易学等特点。\n\n## Java特点\n1. **跨平台**：一次编写，到处运行\n2. **面向对象**：封装、继承、多态\n3. **安全性高**：自动内存管理\n4. **简单易学**：语法类似C++\n\n## 环境搭建\n1. 下载JDK（Java Development Kit）\n2. 配置环境变量JAVA_HOME\n3. 安装IDE（推荐IntelliJ IDEA）\n\n## 第一个程序\n```java\npublic class Hello {\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        System.out.println(\"Hello World\");\n    }\n}\n```"}', 'L1', NOW()),

(0, 'quiz', 'Java简介', '{"questions":[{"content":"Java程序的入口方法是什么？","type":"CHOICE","difficulty":"EASY","options":[{"content":"main()","isCorrect":true},{"content":"start()","isCorrect":false},{"content":"run()","isCorrect":false},{"content":"init()","isCorrect":false}],"analysis":"Java程序的入口是main方法，格式为public static void main(String[] args)"},{"content":"Java是哪个公司开发的？","type":"CHOICE","difficulty":"EASY","options":[{"content":"Microsoft","isCorrect":false},{"content":"Sun Microsystems","isCorrect":true},{"content":"Google","isCorrect":false},{"content":"Oracle","isCorrect":false}],"analysis":"Java由Sun Microsystems于1995年发布，后被Oracle收购"},{"content":"Java的主要特点不包括？","type":"CHOICE","difficulty":"EASY","options":[{"content":"跨平台","isCorrect":false},{"content":"面向对象","isCorrect":false},{"content":"直接操作内存","isCorrect":true},{"content":"安全性高","isCorrect":false}],"analysis":"Java有自动内存管理，不直接操作内存"}]}', 'L1', NOW()),

