(0, 'document', '面向对象编程基础', '{"content":"# 面向对象编程基础\n\n## 类和对象\n```java\nclass Student {\n    String name;\n    int age;\n    \n    void study() {\n        System.out.println(name + \"在学习\");\n    }\n}\n\nStudent s = new Student();\ns.name = \"张三\";\ns.study();\n```\n\n## 三大特性\n1. **封装**：隐藏内部实现\n2. **继承**：代码复用\n3. **多态**：同一行为不同表现\n\n## 构造方法\n```java\nclass Student {\n    String name;\n    \n    Student(String name) {\n        this.name = name;\n    }\n}\n```"}', 'L1', NOW()),

